--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a49675d3da19b054686ae9ecd58461ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: option3 Lumena First
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "Astraeon\u2019s core is unstable. Its energy leaks into the surface, twisting
      the wildlife."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "They were not born hostile. They react to the corruption\u2026 to the
      imbalance."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "They attack anything that carries resonance\u2026 including you."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: Aggressive? what made them aggresive?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: "Since im in the planet the Genetic Sync Device reacted. It registered\u2026
      fluctuations. But I couldn\u2019t identify them."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: Your device senses what lies beneath their corruption. Even if you do not
      yet understand it.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: "When these creatures fall, the energy inside them does not simply vanish.
      It breaks apart\u2026 releasing fragments of what they once carried."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: Fragments? Of what?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9d1852908ff850847b5159c766e754fd, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: Xenocore Elements.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 05ab1f653215476409a566237c2bb668, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: They are echoes of the resonance my people once possessed. Pure elemental
      aspects starfall, tectonic, radiation, and more.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: When a corrupted creature is defeated, the fractured energy escapes. Your
      device will draw it in, stabilize it, and convert it into temporary strength.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Lumena
    text: back to options
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 1
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 5
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b88736a349bfb8e44997cca803c3da53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c0c12ae43e657414daba01b6fa3e183f, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  options: []
  isFinalDialogue: 0
